[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1806","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1806.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1237","title":"Apache smbval SMB认证库 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"smbvalid/smbval SMB 认证库存在多处缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向使用该库的模块（如 Apache::AuthenSmb）发送特制的超长用户名或密码，触发缓冲区溢出，进而执行任意命令。CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。受影响的系统包括所有使用了受影响版本 smbvalid/smbval 库的 Web 服务器及应用，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1237"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:00.657","remediation":"立即停止使用已停止维护的 smbvalid/smbval SMB 认证库及 Apache::AuthenSmb 模块，迁移至 Apache 官方支持的 mod_authnz_ldap 模块通过 LDAP/LDAPS 协议对接 Active Directory 或 Samba DC 完成认证；如仍需 SMB 认证，可改用 Samba Winbind 结合 mod_authnz_ldap 实现，所有输入参数必须经过严格的长度校验与转义处理。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/14384","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2272","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1237.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1237","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1237.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1237.json","https://github.com/openembedded/meta-openembedded/blob/e93799db0e7c7b23da8a00891403425ae7e87d7b/meta-webserver/recipes-httpd/apache2/apache2_2.4.68.bb","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-65fj-56w9-gr9r/GHSA-65fj-56w9-gr9r.json","https://github.com/apache/calcite-avatica/blob/b8bc167268d0900087a24eecd150e8911a6225c0/src/main/config/dependency-check/suppressions.xml","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87828/info.html","https://github.com/anchore/cve-data-enrichment/blob/61a6f60f73f6727dfcef688b4834f32c678de1b5/data/anchore/1999/CVE-1999-1237.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1806.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1800","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1800.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1233","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 域名解析访问限制漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 存在访问限制绕过漏洞。当用户发起初始会话请求且其 IP 地址无法反向解析为 DNS 域名时，IIS 未能正确限制该请求的访问权限，即所谓的\"域名解析\"漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过使用无法解析到 DNS 域名的 IP 地址发起初始会话请求，绕过访问控制策略，获取未授权访问。该漏洞影响 IIS 4.0 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1233"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:00.120","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-039 提供的 IIS 4.0 域限制热修复补丁（KB241562/KB241805），该补丁修正了 IIS 4.0 在 IP 地址无法解析为 DNS 域名时错误放行首次会话请求的问题。由于 IIS 4.0 及 Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，建议升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022）并部署最新版 IIS。临时缓解措施：在 IIS 管理器中禁用基于域名的访问限制策略，改为使用 IP 地址范围限制；同时确保反向 DNS 解析服务正常工作，避免因解析失败导致访问绕过。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q241/5/62.asp","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/657","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-039","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3306","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1233.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1233","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1233.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1233.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-53c2-2qjx-38qh/GHSA-53c2-2qjx-38qh.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/1xxx/cve-1999-1233.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1233.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--f8160a66-e7e6-44ab-9c71-410f00677cdc.json","https://github.com/RiskBasedPrioritization/RiskBasedPrioritizationAnalysis/blob/3d5cc1819ecb8cbc3aeb75d9a8260318544faf56/data_in/acme/acme_cves.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1800.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1709","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1709.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1127","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 命名管道 RPC 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 的命名管道 RPC 连接关闭机制存在缺陷，远程攻击者可通过发送包含畸形数据的连接请求，导致系统无法正常关闭无效的命名管道 RPC 连接，从而引发资源耗尽型拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。微软已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1127"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:46.667","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS98-017 提供的补丁程序（KB195733）。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，建议升级至 Windows Server 2012 或更高版本。临时缓解措施：在防火墙层面阻止对 RPC 服务（TCP/UDP 135 端口）的匿名外部访问，并限制命名管道连接来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q195/7/33.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/523.php","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-017","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1127.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1127","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1127.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1127.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1127.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fjjp-8g8w-55f2/GHSA-fjjp-8g8w-55f2.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86274/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_600_700.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-772.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1709.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1708","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1708.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1094","title":"微软 Internet Explorer MK协议缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 4.01 及更早版本中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向用户发送包含特制长 URL 的链接（使用 \"mk:\" 协议）并诱使用户点击，触发缓冲区溢出，从而在用户系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响范围较广，攻击门槛较低，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1094"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:42.553","remediation":"安装 Microsoft KB Q176697 补丁，或将 Internet Explorer 升级至 4.01 Service Pack 1 及以上版本（如 IE 5.01 SP2）。对于现代系统，建议迁移至 Microsoft Edge 等受支持的浏览器，旧版 IE 已停止安全更新且不再接收补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88480839506155&w=2","http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q176/6/97.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/917","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1094.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1094","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1094.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1094.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1094.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wcrg-6ghq-6288/GHSA-wcrg-6ghq-6288.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88085/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1094.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000992.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1708.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1706","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1706.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1087","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 无点IP地址安全区域绕过漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 4 在处理 URL 中的 32 位无点 IP 地址时存在解析逻辑缺陷，将点分十进制格式以外的纯数字 IP 地址误识别为主机名而非 IP 地址，导致浏览器错误地应用本地 Intranet 区域安全策略。远程攻击者可构造包含无点 IP 地址的恶意 URL，诱使用户访问后绕过正常的安全区隔离，从而执行未授权操作。该漏洞影响 Internet Explorer 4 及早期版本，增大了内网环境下的攻击面。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1087"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:41.647","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 5.0 或更高版本，或改用现代浏览器（如 Edge/Chrome/Firefox）。IE 4 已停止支持且不再接收安全更新，应彻底停止使用。无法升级时可配置代理服务器过滤包含纯数字 IP 的 URL 请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q168/6/17.asp","http://www.microsoft.com/Windows/Ie/security/dotless.asp","http://www.osvdb.org/7828","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-016","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2209","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1087.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1087","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1087.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1087.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1087.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9rv3-rxw8-xr7c/GHSA-9rv3-rxw8-xr7c.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000990.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1087.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--99ba35f8-d4eb-4aae-be83-0d60e01586a1.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1706.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1700","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1700.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1086","title":"Novell NetWare IPX 管理会话伪骗权限提升漏洞","description":"Novell NetWare 5及更早版本在IPX协议上运行且数据包签名级别低于3时存在安全漏洞。远程攻击者可通过伪造IPC分片数据包中的MAC地址来欺骗NetWare核心协议(NCP)调用，从而在未经授权的情况下获取管理员权限。该漏洞危害严重，CVSS评分10.0，可导致目标系统完全受控。建议升级数据包签名级别至3或以上以进行防护。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1086"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:41.520","remediation":"将 NetWare 服务器 NCF 文件中 `SET PACKET SIGNATURE LEVEL` 设置为 3 或更高，强制要求 IPX 数据包签名验证，防止 MAC 地址欺骗攻击。如无法调整签名级别，可考虑禁用 IPX 协议并迁移至 TCP/IP 网络，或使用 VLAN 隔离限制攻击来源。建议升级至 Novell 6 及以上版本以获得完整修复。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93214475111651&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/528","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1086.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1086","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1086.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1086.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1086.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qhf9-4cg8-h46m/GHSA-qhf9-4cg8-h46m.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1086.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000696.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1700.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1689","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1689.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1064","title":"WindowMaker 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"WindowMaker 0.52 至 0.60.0 版本存在多个缓冲区溢出漏洞。当以超长程序名（argv[0]）执行 WindowMaker 时，攻击者可触发缓冲区溢出，导致目标系统拒绝服务，甚至可能执行任意代码。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。受影响版本范围较广，攻击条件简单，无需复杂认证即可利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1064"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-22T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:37.880","remediation":"建议升级 WindowMaker 至 0.61.0 或更高版本，当前最新稳定版 0.96.0 已彻底修复该 argv[0] 缓冲区溢出问题。如无法升级，可采用以下缓解措施：(1) 使用 grsecurity/PaX 内核补丁开启地址空间布局随机化（ASLR）和不可执行内存页（NX）；(2) 在启动包装脚本中校验传入 argv[0] 长度，截断超长程序名后调用 WindowMaker；(3) 禁止在 SetUID 或网络暴露环境中运行 WindowMaker。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93555317429630&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93582070508957&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/596","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1064.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1064","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1064.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1064.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1064.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q8xf-jm9x-c783/GHSA-q8xf-jm9x-c783.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/596/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1064.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1689.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1688","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1688.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1063","title":"CdomainFree whois_raw.cgi 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"tags.<value>CdomainFree 2.4 的 whois_raw.cgi CGI 脚本中存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 fqdn 参数提交包含 shell 元字符的特制请求，在目标服务器上以 Web 服务器权限执行任意命令。该漏洞 CVSS 评分为 10.0，危害等级严重，攻击无需身份认证，可导致服务器完全受控。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1063"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:37.747","remediation":"由于 CdomainFree 2.4 已停止维护，建议立即删除或禁用 whois_raw.cgi 脚本，或在 Web 服务器（Apache/Nginx）层面限制该脚本仅允许可信 IP 访问。同时在 CGI 参数处理中严格过滤 shell 元字符（; | & ` $ ( ) { } < >），并对 fqdn 参数实施白名单验证（仅允许域名合法字符），从根本上防止命令注入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/14019","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/304","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2251","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19242","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1063.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1063","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1063.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1063.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1063.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/whois_raw.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/304/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1063.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1688.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1688.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1688.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1687","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1687.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1055","title":"Microsoft Excel 97 工作表函数任意代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Excel 97 在调用工作表函数前未向用户发出安全警告，攻击者可通过构造包含恶意 CALL 函数的 XLS 文件诱导用户打开，利用 CALL 函数加载并执行恶意 DLL，从而在目标系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Excel 97 及后续兼容版本，攻击者可通过社会工程方式诱导受害者打开特制文档触发，无需身份认证。目前已存在公开利用代码，危害较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1055"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:36.767","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS98-018 提供的补丁程序，该补丁可通过 https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-018 获取。同时在 Excel 中将宏安全级别设置为\"高\"以阻止未签名的 CALL 函数执行，并建议升级到 Office 2000 及以上版本以彻底规避该问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/179","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-018","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1737","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1055.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1055","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1055.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1055.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1055.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cx75-p9pm-2q97/GHSA-cx75-p9pm-2q97.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_600_700.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-356.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1055.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1687.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1686","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1686.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1053","title":"Matt Wright Guestbook.pl 服务端包含命令执行漏洞","description":"Matt Wright Guestbook.pl 2.3.1 存在服务器端包含（SSI）命令注入漏洞。该脚本试图通过移除 \"<!--\" 与 \"-->\" 分隔符之间的内容来过滤用户插入的 SSI 命令，但由于 Apache 1.3.9 及部分其他版本允许除 \"-->\" 以外的其他闭合序列，导致过滤机制可被绕过。远程攻击者可通过在留言内容中插入特制的 SSI 指令，在服务器上执行任意命令，进而获取系统控制权。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1053"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:36.507","remediation":"立即停用 Matt Wright Guestbook.pl 2.3.1 及更早版本，替换为受支持的留言板程序（如用现代 PHP/Python 实现的替代品）。在 Apache 配置中对 guestbook.pl 所在目录禁用 Server-Side Include：`Options -Includes`，或通过 `RemoveHandler .shtml` 关闭 SSI 解析。如暂时无法更换，可添加 Apache rewrite 规则阻止包含 `<!--#` 的请求。同时建议在系统层面对 CGI 目录启用 `open_basedir` 等沙箱限制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/33674","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/82/27296","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/82/27560","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/776","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/9907","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1053.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/1fb9a053a31c41206e693c4b4856611d722d4df7/1999/CVE-1999-1053.json","https://github.com/rix4uni/cvemapping/blob/3fc9c3bcaeabe40a6c524b4856d657e849f9160b/1999/CVE-1999-1053/CVE-1999-1053-PoC.py","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1053","https://github.com/ycdxsb/PocOrExp_in_Github/blob/1b8090ba645ab1c5dda