.0/4.0、MDAC 2.1 等组件，攻击无需身份认证，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。微软已发布安全公告及补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1011"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.110","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-025 提供的补丁，或升级至 Windows 2000 及以上版本（默认禁用 RDS DataFactory）。如无法升级，删除注册表键 `HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\W3SVC\\Parameters\\ADCLaunch\\RDSServer.DataFactory` 以禁用该危险组件，同时在 IIS 管理器中移除 `/msadc/` 虚拟目录映射。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-054.shtml","http://www.osvdb.org/272","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-004","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-025","https://www.securityfocus.com/bid/529","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19424","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1011.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1011","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/e4734a5d374932e0e8adfb714d6049181237b752/1999/CVE-1999-1011/README.md","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/968abdc74763b43a3cdd216fbb1950cab484f982/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1011.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1011.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1011.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qcm7-2qvw-4c58/GHSA-qcm7-2qvw-4c58.json","https://github.com/decal/werdlists/blob/81edb463f7f6311c85defefaf75ac9cd58e5cfb9/exploit-info/symantec-attack-signatures.txt","https://github.com/Chudry/Xerror/blob/07ec57cabcd27cdb47c89af452bdf4ed07207347/xerror/parsing/msf_module_result/msf_module_cve.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1683.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1683.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1683.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1682","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1682.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0997","title":"WU-FTPD FTP Conversion 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"WU-FTPD 2.4.2至2.6.2版本中启用了FTP文件转换功能时存在命令执行漏洞。攻击者可通过上传包含特殊畸形文件名的文件，该文件名在传输过程中被作为参数传递给转换程序（如tar或uncompress），从而导致任意命令在服务器端执行。该漏洞影响多版本WU-FTPD服务器，CVSS评分7.5，危害等级高危。攻击者无需身份认证，仅需具备FTP上传权限即可触发。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0997"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.343","remediation":"升级至 wu-ftpd 2.6.3 或更高版本以修复此漏洞；若无法升级，在 ftpaccess 配置文件中关闭 conversion 功能，注释或移除相关 conversion 规则，并限制匿名用户上传目录不可执行转换操作。作为临时缓解措施，可移除 tar、uncompress 等转换程序的 setuid 权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.debian.org/security/2003/dsa-377","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20563","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0997.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0997","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0997.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0997.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2hff-p384-25wq/GHSA-2hff-p384-25wq.json","https://g